comments: Green (PHI) maintains a legal vertical position as he defends Harrell's (LAL) shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Kuzma's (LAL) path and does not deliver any contact.
Kuzma (LAL) and Harris (PHI) make marginal contact with each other as they engage prior to the steal.
Schroder (LAL) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Simmons (PHI) during the drive.
Simmons (PHI) reaches in and makes incidental hand on ball contact to dislodge the ball from Harrell (LAL) in the post.
Green (PHI) maintains a legal defensive position and absorbs the contact as Schroder (LAL) lowers his shoulder and dribbles into Green at the end of the drive.
Simmons' (PHI) foot incidentally makes contact with the ball during the loose ball.
Schroder (LAL) makes marginal contact with Harris (PHI) during the drive.
Schroder (LAL) legally contests Curry's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Green (PHI) is late establishing himself in Kuzma's (LAL) path on Kuzma's driving shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes foot to foot contact with himself during the drive. Schroder (LAL) does not make any contact with Simmons that affects his SQBR.
Kuzma (LAL) legally contests Green's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Following the pass, Harrell (LAL) turns and makes marginal contact with Green (PHI).
Scott (PHI) legally contests Kuzma's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Harrell (LAL) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Harrell (LAL) extends his backside into Thybulle's (PHI) path and makes marginal contact with Thybulle during the pick.
Scott (PHI) makes contact with the ball then marginal follow-through contact with Schroder's (LAL) hand during Schroder's driving shot attempt.
